                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Allowing for 1% statistical uncertainty,",
                " less than 0.5% uncertainty from Compton scattering,",
                " about 0.5% uncertainties in the efficiency and",
                " calibration of the Faraday cup, and uncertainties of",
                " about 0.2% arising from the target thickness, the",
                " time constant, timing errors, and beam fluctuations.",
                "Systematic uncertainties from secondary particle",
                " interactions in the target, losses of carbon-11 during",
                " and after the bombardment, and gas loss of carbon-11",
                " were expected to be much less than 1 per-cent and were",
                " neglected."
